7 TROUBLESHOOTING

How can I play VETTE! against another person?
You can play head-to-head in two ways: direct connect or using a modem. If you
connect two computers together directly, a null-modem serial cable must be
connected to each computer's serial port. The null-modem serial cable must have
pins 2 and 3 switched and the pin for the ground must be straight through. If
you're connecting two computers over phone lines, you need two 1200 baud (or
faster) Hayes-compatible modems.

